            <span class="headingBackground">Reference</span>
          </h3>
          <p>
            Naidoo RJ, Williams HC. <a href="http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/pde.12215/abstract" title="Link to article">Therapeutic use of stories for children with atopic eczema and other chronic skin conditions</a>. Pediatr Dermatol. 2013 Nov-Dec;30(6):765-7. doi: 10.1111/pde.12215. Epub 2013 Sep 23.
